===Etymology===
*From: '''司馬昭之心''', [[路人]][[皆]][[知]]
Literally: (Even the people in the street know) the heart of [[w:Sima Zhao|Sima Zhao]]

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' sīmăzhāo zhī xīn)
# evil ambitions that are transparent to everyone

